OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,FA "catalogue of failings" lead to the
OL,8,Fdeaths of two care home residents who
OL,9,Fwere strapped into their wheelchairs
OL,10,Fon a boat trip and dragged to the
OL,11,Fbottom of a lake when the boat
OL,12,Fcapsized, a report has found.
OL,14,FAlison Tilsley, 63, and Alexander
OL,15,FWood, 43, were "thrown" into the water
OL,16,Fat Roadford Lake, near Okehampton in
OL,17,FWest Devon, and sank so rapidly they
OL,18,Fcould not be saved. Their bodies were
OL,19,Frecovered the following day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
