OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,FA third resident was pulled from the
OL,8,Fwater not breathing but survived after
OL,9,Freceiving CPR at the scene before
OL,10,Fbeing flown to hospital.
OL,12,FAn investigation by the Marine
OL,13,FAccident Investigation Branch (MAIB)
OL,14,Fhas now revealed the boat they were on
OL,15,Fwas "poorly maintained" and leaking.
OL,16,FIt also found "no-one" had considered
OL,17,Fthe risk of taking wheelchair users
OL,18,Fout onto the water.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
