OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,FThe incident happened on 8 June 2022
OL,8,Fwhen staff from Burdon Grange care
OL,9,Fhome took six of its residents for a
OL,10,Fday trip to the South West Lake Trust
OL,11,Factivity centre at the lake.
OL,13,FThe group was split into two, with the
OL,14,Ffirst group made up of two members of
OL,15,Fcare home staff and three residents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
