OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,FThey were all given buoyancy aids and
OL,8,Floaded onto the Wheelyboat 123. The
OL,9,Fvessel was provided by the Wheelyboat
OL,10,FTrust - a UK charity that supplies
OL,11,Fgroups and organisations with
OL,12,Fwheelchair-accessible boats.
OL,14,FBut the report says the Wheelyboat 123
OL,15,Fwas poorly maintained and water leaked
OL,16,Fon board, causing the boat to capsize.
OL,18,F"The occupants of the boat were thrown
OL,19,Finto the water during the capsize,"
OL,20,Fthe report says.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
