OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,F"The two residents were strapped into
OL,8,Ftheir motorised wheelchairs and
OL,9,Frapidly sank to the bottom of the lake
OL,10,Fwhen they were thrown into the water
OL,11,Fand could not be rescued."
OL,13,FThe report says Ms Tilsley, who had
OL,14,Flimited motor skills due to a
OL,15,Fneurological disorder, initially
OL,16,Fgrabbed her carer's hand as they were
OL,17,Fboth dragged below the surface.
OL,19,FBut Ms Tilsley's motorised wheelchair
OL,20,Fweighed 124kg and she let go of the
OL,21,Fcarer's hand before sinking rapidly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
