OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,FMr Wood, who had severe and complex
OL,8,Fcare needs due to a blood clot on his
OL,9,Fbrain following a head injury, was
OL,10,Fsimilarly dragged down by his
OL,11,Fwheelchair, which weighed 117kg.
OL,13,FThe third resident, who had multiple
OL,14,Fsclerosis, had been in a manual
OL,15,Fwheelchair weighing 18kg. They were
OL,16,Fpulled from the water not breathing by
OL,17,Fthe centre's visitor experience
OL,18,Fmanager. Despite being in a critical
OL,19,Fcondition, they survived after being
OL,20,Fgiven CPR and receiving hospital
OL,21,Ftreatment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
