OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,FThe MAIB report says both the activity
OL,8,Fcentre and the care home had "assumed"
OL,9,Fthe other party knew about managing
OL,10,Fthe activity for disabled people. It
OL,11,Fadds that the risks of strapping the
OL,12,Fresidents into their chairs were
OL,13,F"neither considered nor mitigated".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
