OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,FChief Inspector of Marine Accidents
OL,8,FAndrew Moll OBE said the boat trips
OL,9,Fwere "beneficial" for residents but
OL,10,Fsaid "no one had taken time to
OL,11,Fproperly consider the risks"
OL,12,Fassociated with taking the wheelchair
OL,13,Fusers on the water - either before the
OL,14,Faccident or on the day itself.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
