OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,FHe added: "The condition of the
OL,8,FWheelyboat had been allowed to
OL,9,Fdeteriorate so water could enter it,
OL,10,Fand on the day no-one recognised the
OL,11,Fimplications of carrying vulnerable
OL,12,Fpeople who were strapped into heavy
OL,13,Fmotorised wheelchairs around a lake in
OL,14,Fan open boat. In short, no one had
OL,15,Ftheir eye on the risk, and tragically
OL,16,FAlison Tilsley and Alex Wood lost
OL,17,Ftheir lives.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
