OL,3,CTwo killed in boat capsize were
OL,4,Cstrapped to wheelchairs and 'dragged'
OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,F"As well as the catalogue of failings
OL,8,Fhighlighted by the report, the
OL,9,Finvestigation has also uncovered a
OL,10,Fworrying lack of oversight which must
OL,11,Fbe seen as an impetus for urgent
OL,12,Faction. Charitable activities such as
OL,13,Fthis seem to fall into a grey zone
OL,14,Fwith no organisation or authority in a
OL,15,Fposition of oversight. This meant that
OL,16,Fno one stepped in to question what had
OL,17,Fbecome custom and practice. Addressing
OL,18,Fthis is not simple and may only be
OL,19,Fpossible with a change in the law;
OL,20,Fhowever, the current situation is not
OL,21,Fsomething that should be tolerated."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
