OL,5,Cto lakebed
OL,7,FThe South West Lakes Trust said its
OL,8,Fthoughts also remain with those
OL,9,Faffected by the "tragedy".
OL,11,FIts chief executive James Platts said
OL,12,Fthe Trust is reviewing the report and
OL,13,Fwill implement its recommendations.
OL,15,F"We welcome the publication of this
OL,16,Freport and recognise that its aim is
OL,17,Fnot to assign blame or liability, but
OL,18,Fto improve water safety and ensure, as
OL,19,Ffar as possible, that future accidents
OL,20,Fare prevented," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
