OL,7,FHe added: "We continue to operate our
OL,8,Fother activities under the
OL,9,Faccreditation of the Royal Yachting
OL,10,FAssociation and the Adventure
OL,11,FActivities Licensing Authority. Whilst
OL,12,Fwe immediately ceased the use of
OL,13,FWheelyboats on our waters following
OL,14,Fthe incident, we recognise the
OL,15,Fbenefits vessels of this type provide
OL,16,Fto those with disabilities and will
OL,17,Fconsider the future operation of such
OL,18,Fvessels in the context of the
OL,19,Frecommendations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
