OL,7,F"It would be inappropriate for us to
OL,8,Fcomment further while other
OL,9,Finvestigations continue."
OL,11,FIn a statement, The Wheelyboat Trust
OL,12,Fsaid its "heartfelt sympathies and
OL,13,Fcondolences remain with the families
OL,14,Fand friends of those who died".
OL,16,FThe spokesperson said the charity has
OL,17,Fworked with the MAIB throughout the
OL,18,Finvestigation, adding: "They did not
OL,19,Ffind that the design of the vessel
OL,20,Finvolved contributed to the incident.
